"Recycling cardboard makes sense as it conserves natural resources and is cheaper than incinerating it in the waste-to-energy plant. The collected cardboard is an essential raw material for the production of corrugated cardboard, packaging, and even furniture. Because the technical processing continues to improve, even high-quality cardboard products are made from recycled cardboard." = "回收紙板具有實際意義，因為它能節約自然資源，而且比在廢棄物發電廠焚化處理更便宜。收集到的紙板是生產瓦楞紙板、包裝材料，甚至是家具的重要原料。隨著技術加工的持續進步，即使是高品質的紙板產品，現在也能由回收紙板製成。";
