"The Mobile Recycling Center (Mobiler Recyclinghof) brings recycling services directly to your neighborhood. You can drop off bulky waste, electronic devices, metals, and other recyclables. It replaces the former Cargo Tram and E-Tram services, offering a convenient and accessible way to recycle materials that don't belong in regular household waste." = "行動回收中心（Mobiler Recyclinghof）將回收服務直接送到您的社區。您可以在此丟棄大型廢棄物、電子設備、金屬及其他可回收物。它取代了先前的貨運電車和電動電車服務，為回收不屬於一般家庭垃圾的物品提供了一種便利且易於取得的方式。";
"The waste must be disposed of in a blue Zuri bag. The blue Zuri bag is available for a fee in retail stores and comes in 10, 17, 35, 60, or 110-liter sizes. Place your Zuri bag container at the designated pickup location before 7 a.m. on the collection day." = "廢棄物必須使用藍色 Zuri 袋處理。藍色 Zuri 袋可在零售店付費購買，有 10、17、35、60 或 110 公升等尺寸。請於收集日早上 7 點前，將您的 Zuri 袋容器放置於指定的收集地點。";
"The Zurich Waste Disposal and Recycling brings over 30,000 Zuri bags to the Hagenholz waste-to-energy plant every day, where they are environmentally burned. The heat generated from incineration produces ecological power and climate-friendly Zurich heat, which can heat around 170,000 apartments." = "蘇黎世廢物處理及回收公司每日將超過 30,000 個蘇黎世專用垃圾袋運送至 Hagenholz 廢物發電廠進行環保焚燒。焚燒產生的熱能轉化為環保電力和對氣候友善的蘇黎世市區供暖，足以為約 170,000 套公寓供暖。";
