"Use of CasaZurich is governed by Apple's Standard EULA for apps. Subscriptions will automatically renew unless canceled within 24-hours before the end of the current period. You can cancel anytime with your iTunes account settings. Any unused portion of a free trial will be forfeited if you purchase a subscription. Auto-renewal may be turned off by the user, by going to the user's Account Settings after purchase. The duration and price of each subscription is displayed on the purchase screen, and updated at the time of purchase. If you have any questions about CasaZurich Terms of Use, please reach out to me at support@casazurigo.ch" = "使用 CasaZurich 受 Apple 的應用程式標準最終用戶授權協議 (EULA) 管轄。訂閱服務將於當前週期結束前 24 小時內未取消時自動續訂。您可隨時透過您的 iTunes 帳戶設定取消訂閱。若您購買訂閱服務，免費試用期內任何未使用的部分將被沒收。購買後，使用者可前往其帳戶設定關閉自動續訂功能。各訂閱方案的持續時間和價格均顯示於購買畫面，並於購買時更新。如果您對 CasaZurich 的使用條款有任何疑問，請透過 support@casazurigo.ch 與我聯繫。";
"Use of CasaZurich is governed by Google Play's Standard EULA for apps. CasaZurich is free to use. Optional donations to support development are available in the app settings. If you have any questions about CasaZurich Terms of Use, please reach out to me at support@casazurigo.ch" = "CasaZurich 的使用受 Google Play 應用程式標準最終使用者授權協議（EULA）規範。CasaZurich 可免費使用。您可在應用程式設定中選擇性捐款以支持開發。若您對 CasaZurich 使用條款有任何疑問，請透過 support@casazurigo.ch 與我聯繫。";
